storage and disposal facility in andrews texas the company offers engineered components ranging from locks utilized in ignition systems office furniture and postal boxes to precision slides used in filing cabinets bottom mount freezers and tool boxes to ergonomic keyboard arms and flat panel monitor mounts as well as gauges and exhaust systems for highperformance boats in addition it supplies titanium met contran corporation inc through its subsidiaries manufactures and sells titanium dioxide pigments in north america and europe it also offers manufacturing engineering components in the areas of security products furniture components and marine and operating a treatment storage and disposal facility in andrews texas the company offers engineered components ranging from locks utilized in ignition systems office furniture and postal boxes to precision slides used in filing cabinets bottom mount freezers and tool boxes to ergonomic keyboard arms and flat panel monitor mounts as well as gauges and exhaust systems for highperformance boats in addition it supplies titanium metal products to aerospace and industrial applications the company offers solutions for the management of radioactive hazardous and mixed materials to government organizations department of energy department of defense environmental protection agency army corps of engineers and commercial entities in the united states it has titanium dioxide pigment manufacturing sites in north america and europe contran corporation inc was incorporated in  and is based in dallas texas detailed description  lyndon b johnson freewaythree lincoln centresuite dallas tx united statesfounded in  phone  fax  key executives for contran corporation inc contran corporation inc does not have any key executives recorded similar private companies by industry company name region x technology llc united states  custom molded plasticsltd united states st century plastics corporation united states n inc united states th generation res