ship in marketing and  million for the presidents scholars program the harold simmons foundation is the philanthropic arm of the simmons financial empire two of simmons daughters serena simmons connelly and lisa simmons epstein are its administrators the foundation supports the causes of immigration rights campaign reform prison reform handgun control and reproductive rights the contributions to the presidential bids of hillary clinton and barack obama made by serena simmons connelly were privately made not funded by the foundation simmons donated money to help fund the hobbyeberly telescope dark energy experiment at the university of texas he has previously given to ut athletic programs and the mccombs school of business by  total donations from his family and foundation to the ut southwestern medical center at dallas exceeded  million in  simmons pledged  million to the george w bush presidential library contingent upon its being located at smu in  harold simmons made a grant to the young americas foundation to establish the harold simmons lecture series which enabled former us senator zell miller to tour college campuses during the  school year to promote his message in defense of america from foreign and domestic threats to our freedom since mid  simmons has given funds to a chronic kidney disease research team led by dr kamyar kalantarzadeh to examine predictors of longevity in chronic kidney disease subsequently the “harold simmons center for chronic disease research and epidemiology” was created first in “los angeles biomedical research institute” at “harborucla medical center” then in uc irvine medical center at university of california irvine school of medicine in orange ca which has published a large number of scientific reports and articles in  oprah winfrey announced that harold and annette simmons her neighbors in montecito california had contributed  million to her oprah winfrey leadership academy for girls in south africa in  harold and annette simmons announced a  million gift to southern methodist university to provide an endowment for the universitys school of education and human development the gift allocated  million for construction of a new facility to be named the annette caldwell simmons building  million for graduate student fellowships and  million for faculty support and an endowed deanship in  the harold simmons foundation made a donation of  million to the dallas zoo the largest single private contribution in the zoos year history annette and harold simmons have been underwriters for  consecutive years to the dallas crystal charity ball fashion show and luncheon the crystal charity ball has distributed more than  million to childrens charities since  the harold simmons foundation is a major donor of over  to the dallas womens foundation which commissioned a study of womens economic security in the county dallasarlingtonfort worth metropolitan area the harold simmons foundation issued a  million challenge grant to the parkland memorial hospital foundation to aid in fundraising to build a new public hospital one of the largest private gifts for a public hospital campaign in the nation the harold simmons foundation made a gift to the legal hospice of texas a nonprofit law firm providing compassionate legal services at no charge to lowincome individuals who are terminally ill in  and  awardsedit charles cameron sprague community service award annette g strauss humanitarian award  angel of freedom awardharold simmons foundation human rights initiative personal lifeedit simmons has been married three times his first wife walked out on him in  leaving him with custody of their two daughters scheryle simmons patigian born  lisa simmons epstein born  his second wife was sandra k saliba sandra would later become braniff airlines first female pilotthey divorced in  they had two children andrea leigh simmons swanson born  serena sha simmons connelly born  in june  he married his third and last wife annette caldwell fleck born  an interior designer with two children from a previous marriage she is a native of tyler texas and a graduate of southern methodist university after graduating she taught second and third grade in dallas and at clark field a us air base in the philippines in october  mrs simmons was featured on the oprah television show giving a tour of simmons boyhood town golden texas during its sweet potato festival in another episode annettes tea party mrs simmons entertainment style was a feature referencesedit  forbes the worlds billionaires  harold simmons september   conflicts of interest and special committees revisited has kahn v tremont corp permanently changed the landscape or merely slightly altered it findlawcom  richard kimble philanthropist harold simmons libertas young americas foundation   richard kimble philanthropist harold simmons establishes lecture series featuring senator zell miller  richard kimble philanthropist harold simmons establishes lecture series featuring senator zel miller libertas young americas foundation   a b c historical marker society of america reuben leon and fairess clark simmons retrieved december    bill bancroft perils of the simmons watch new york times december    ledgerwood sloan harold simmons builds  million empire dallas morning news december    a b harold simmons smu news november    kimble young americas foundation   james lehrer protesting students sit in walk picket line at store dallas morning news january    harold simmons international directory of company histories vol  st james press   a b simmons donates  million for cancer research andrew county news january    bill bancroft perils of the simmons watch new york times december    thomas hayes lockheed fends off simmons the new york times march    richard w stevenson simmons is considering possible lockheed bid new york times february   simmons to lift lockheed stake new york times november    raider to trader  rising oil prices bring gushing profits to 